metadata.description:
Created by Denver_Donkey & the powers of AI, DONKs is a collection of 150 Cartoon Donkeys.

DONKs have made their way onto the eth blockchain to collaborate with collectors & fellow artists.  

DONKs holders can:
1.)  Submit a name and lore for their DONK.  DD will update the metadata to reflect these changes.  

2.)  Receive early access to future DD drops, events & experiences.  DONKs is for the NFT community. 

3.)  Upgrade their DONK to an animated version for .05ETH!  
*** One lucky DONK holder will get their upgrade for free! ***

Limit 3 per drop/ 3 per wallet
